title: Do You Love Me?
author: Boston Dynamics
description: Our whole crew got together to celebrate the start of what we hope will be a happier year:  Happy New Year from all of us at Boston Dynamics.  www.BostonDynamics.com.

localize.description: 我们全体工作人员齐聚一堂，庆祝我们希望更快乐的一年的开始：来自波士顿动力公司所有人的新年快乐。www.BostonDynamics.com。
localize.title: 你爱我吗？
